text: What brings you in today
I've been feeling worn out all the time, and my legs swell up pretty bad.
How long is it been going on
It's been a while now, probably a few months. things just seem to be getting worse.
Is anything seem to make it any better or worse
Not really. resting doesn't seem to help much, and i haven't noticed anything that makes it worse either. it's just there all the time.
Any other places swelling up besides your legs
Mostly just my legs, but my face looks puffier than usual lately.
Have you been experiencing any pain
Yeah, i've got this deep ache in my bones, like i've been hauling pipe all day.
On a scale of 1 to 10 how bad is the pain
I'd say it's around a 6 most days. it's there, but i can still manage.
Located
The pain's mostly in my arms and legs.
Are you having any change in your urinary habits
Yeah, i pee less than i used to, and sometimes it's darker.
Have you noticed any blood in your urine
No, i haven't seen any blood in my urine.
Any weight changes
I've dropped some weight without trying. food doesn't sit right anymore.
How much have you lost
I'm not exactly sure, but it's enough that my clothes fit looser.
Did you have any other symptoms come on around the time of the night or of the swelling
My legs twitch a lot at night, and i wake up with this white powder on my skin.
Debbie back pain
I have a deep ache in my bones, but it's not specific to my back.
Have you had any fevers or chills
I get cold sometimes and then sweat out of nowhere, but i haven't noticed any fevers.
Any night sweats
Yeah, i wake up drenched in sweat sometimes.
Do you have any product medical conditions
I've had high blood pressure since my thirties, and i had a mild stroke a while back.
What medicines do you take
I've got a whole bunch of medicines i'm on that i can't pronounce. my girlfriend makes me keep a list in my wallet.
Can we see it
Sure, the list includes furosemide, nifedipine, potassium chloride, clonidine patch, clopidogrel, atenolol, iron, and aspirin.
Have you ever been hospitalized or had a surgery
I haven't had any surgeries, but i was hospitalized before for lung congestion and after i had a mild stroke.
When did that happen
The stroke happened a while back, but i can't remember the exact date. the lung congestion was a bit before that.
Do you have any family medical history of any conditions
Yeah, my dad had high blood pressure and diabetes, and my mom had breast cancer.
Do you have any allergies
None that i know of.
Have you had any trauma or injury
No, i haven't had any recent trauma or injuries.
What is your occupation
I'm a plumber, but i've been off work lately because i'm too weak to keep up with the jobs.
Are you aware of any exposures you had from your occupation
Not that i know of. i haven't been around anything unusual at work.
Do you use tobacco
No, i don't smoke.
Do you use alcohol
I go out for a few beers on fridays sometimes, but not often.
Do you use any drugs
No, i don't use drugs.
Have you noticed any skin changes
Yeah, i wake up with this white powder on my skin, and i've noticed bruises showing up for no reason.
Have you felt dizzy or lightheaded
Yeah, i get dizzy if i stand up too fast.
Are you sure of breath
Yeah, i get short of breath when i walk too far or climb stairs.
Do you have any headaches
I don't really get headaches much.
Do you have any changes in your vision
Bright lights bother me, and my girlfriend says my eyes look like they're bulging a bit.
Have you felt confused or lost lately
Yeah, sometimes i get mixed up or forget what i was doing.
Are you feeling any changes in temperature any hot or cold that you don't normally feel
I feel cold sometimes and then sweat out of nowhere, but no major changes in how i handle temperatures.
Do you have any change in your appetite
Yeah, food doesn't sit right anymore, and i've been eating less.
Have you had to urinate more frequently or less frequently
I pee less frequently than i used to.
Have you been more thirsty or less thirsty than normal
I haven't noticed any big changes in how thirsty i am.
Have you felt nauseous or vomited lately
Yeah, i feel like throwing up most days, and i've vomited a few times lately.
Have you had any constipation or diarrhea
No, i haven't had any constipation or diarrhea.
What is your taste like
Everything tastes like metal to me lately.
Interesting
Yeah, it's strange and not very pleasant. anything else you'd like to know?
